<template>
<v-form ref="form" lazy-validation>
  <v-row>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-text-field 
      	v-model="user_id" 
        label="아이디*" 
        :rules="user_id_rule" 
        :disabled="state == 'ins' ? false : true"
        required
        ></v-text-field>
    </v-col>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-text-field 
      	v-model="user_nm" 
        label="이름*" 
        :rules="user_nm_rule" 
        required
        ></v-text-field>
    </v-col>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-text-field 
      	v-model="user_pw" 
        label="비밀번호*" 
        type="password" 
        :rules="user_pw_rule"
        ></v-text-field>
    </v-col>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-text-field 
      	v-model="user_pw_chk" 
        label="비밀번호 확인*" 
        type="password" 
        :rules="user_pw_rule2"
        ></v-text-field>
    </v-col>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-select 
      	v-model="user_auth" 
        label="권한*" 
        :items="authList" 
        item-text="name" 
        item-value="value" 
        return-object
        :rules="user_auth_rule"
        ></v-select>
    </v-col>
    <v-col cols="12">
      <v-text-field 
      	v-model="user_desc" 
        label="설명" 
        :rules="user_desc_rule"
        ></v-text-field>
    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</v-form>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "HelloWorld",
  props: {
    msg: String,
  },
};
</script>
